rp-goals-ui-title = Personal round goal
rp-goals-ui-subtitle = Choose one RP-safe goal. This is a voluntary roleplay prompt, not a server order.
rp-goals-ui-accept = Select
rp-goals-ui-reroll = Reroll ({$count} left)
rp-goals-selection-confirmed = Personal goal selected: {$goal}
rp-goals-character-info-entry = Personal RP goal: {$goal}

rp-goal-service-paperwork-excellence = Keep your workspace in exemplary order and noticeably improve at least one routine process.
rp-goal-medical-warm-reception = Make medical care feel clear and calm for the crew: explain what is happening and what comes next to at least several patients.
rp-goal-engineering-preventive-checks = Perform a preventive inspection and fix at least one potential problem before it becomes an emergency.
rp-goal-science-share-knowledge = Share useful knowledge from your department with the crew through conversation, an announcement, or a demonstration.
rp-goal-cargo-organized-delivery = Organize deliveries so that at least one order or request is handled quickly, clearly, and without confusion.
rp-goal-command-support-crew = Take time to meaningfully support at least one crew member with resources, advice, or coordination.
rp-goal-security-visible-patrol = Perform a visible, calm patrol and help prevent at least one conflict without escalation.
rp-goal-unsafe-sabotage-example = Break something important and do not get caught.
